<div class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-7xl px-6 sm:px-8">
  <!-- Content section -->
  <div class="mx-auto -mt-12 max-w-7xl px-6 sm:mt-0 lg:px-8 xl:-mt-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Our mission</h2>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col gap-x-8 gap-y-20 lg:flex-row">
        <div class="lg:w-full lg:max-w-2xl lg:flex-auto">
          <p class="text-xl leading-8 text-gray-600">Poor Man with a Pan was started to keep track of the recipes I love to cook. It has grown into a resource that I hope will become a go-to source for thousands of people looking for delicious and affordable recipes.</p>
          <div class="mt-10 max-w-xl text-base leading-7 text-gray-700">
            <p>Whether you're a seasoned chef or just starting out, our mission is to provide you with simple, tasty, and budget-friendly recipes that anyone can make. We believe that cooking should be fun, accessible, and rewarding for everyone.</p>
            <p class="mt-10">We are constantly exploring new recipes and techniques to share with our community. Our goal is to inspire you to get creative in the kitchen and enjoy the process of cooking, no matter your skill level.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:flex lg:flex-auto lg:justify-center">
          <dl class="w-64 space-y-8 xl:w-80">
            <div class="flex flex-col-reverse gap-y-4">
              <dt class="text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Recipes added</dt>
              <dd class="text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900">200+</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col-reverse gap-y-4">
              <dt class="text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Monthly visitors</dt>
              <dd class="text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900">10,000+</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col-reverse gap-y-4">
              <dt class="text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Community members</dt>
              <dd class="text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900">5,000+</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Image section -->
  <div class="mt-32 sm:mt-40 xl:mx-auto xl:max-w-7xl xl:px-8">
    <%= image_tag "table-dinner.webp", alt: "Table with dinner", class: "aspect-[5/2] w-full object-cover xl:rounded-3xl" %>
  </div>

  <!-- Values section -->
  <div class="mx-auto mt-32 max-w-7xl px-6 sm:mt-40 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Our values</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">At Poor Man with a Pan, we are guided by a few key principles that shape everything we do.</p>
    </div>
    <dl class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 text-base leading-7 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div>
        <dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Simplicity</dt>
        <dd class="mt-1 text-gray-600">We believe that great food doesn't have to be complicated. Our recipes are easy to follow and use simple, accessible ingredients.</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Community</dt>
        <dd class="mt-1 text-gray-600">We are building a supportive community of food enthusiasts who share a love for cooking and learning from one another.</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Creativity</dt>
        <dd class="mt-1 text-gray-600">We encourage creativity in the kitchen. Our recipes are a starting pointâ€”feel free to make them your own!</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Affordability</dt>
        <dd class="mt-1 text-gray-600">We focus on recipes that are budget-friendly without compromising on taste or quality.</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Learning</dt>
        <dd class="mt-1 text-gray-600">Cooking is a journey, and we are committed to learning and sharing new techniques and recipes along the way.</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Enjoyment</dt>
        <dd class="mt-1 text-gray-600">Above all, we believe that cooking should be enjoyable. We hope to bring joy to your kitchen with every recipe.</dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>
</div>